---
title: Sticky Hoisin Chicken Thighs with Roasted Broccoli and Red Onion
description: Sticky, zesty and rich with umami flavour, our hoisin sticky baked chicken thighs are just the thing when you’re after a no-frills dinner but still want maximum flavour. Simply pop in the ingredients in a roasting tray for the ultimate time-saving recipe!
